lyrics:
[Verse]
In this city, a hero once stood tall
With powers that could conquer one and all
But now he's bidding his farewell goodbye
Leaving us with tears falling from the sky

[Chorus]
Oh, our superhero, please don't go away
Your strength and courage forever we'll pray
You fought for justice, our hearts will forever pine
Oh, our superhero, you'll always shine

Note
This song follows the requested structure and contains one verse followed by one chorus, each consisting of four lines
